sections.Trivia:
- The flowers' painting in Furitsukaya Ryokan is from Your Best Friend.
- The culprit's pistol is a SIG-Sauer P226.
- The suspects' names come from "social media"[1] :
Tamami Mitsui (光井 珠実) comes from Twitter (ツイッター ,Tsuittā?) ;
Shinobu Yuchi (湯地 志信) comes from Youtube (ユーチューブ ,Yūchūbu?) ;
Sumika Nihei (二瓶 純夏) comes from Facebook (フェイスブック ,Feisubukku?) ;
Isao Sawaguri (沢栗 勲) comes from GREE (グリー ,Gurī?) ;
Miku Sawaguri (沢栗 未紅) comes from GREE (グリー ,Gurī?) and mixi (ミクシイ ,mikushī?) ;
Additionally, the hot springs resort "Furitsukaya" (降塚屋) comes from Flickr (フリッカ ,Furikka?).
